{"tid":1513211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（反送中數據資料總結）跪求巴絲入黎幫手","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T15:10:55.000Z","uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"faa8fe8021128588fec4b40d4124a0a48dcd5b2f","tid":1513211,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"要麻煩大家 對於我之後整文宣好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前我係某啲post見過有人打過一啲整合關於由開始到現在所影響嘅人有幾多：（格式如下）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經歷  日：<br />\n有 位義士失去眼睛 <br />\n有 位義士被捕<br />\n有 位義士已經犧牲生命<br />\n超過 位示威者受傷</span></strong><br />\n等等......可以再加<br />\n<br />\n如果邊位巴絲有以上資訊 麻煩一齊填左佢<br />\n又或者你見過邊到有就copy比我 非常感謝<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccx9GyO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fccx9GyO.jpg&h=b781933f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85456405901d1d47d7dab8a4a3f16fcea82af4af","tid":1513211,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"3ecfff60cb1a89e88600610e52ca71452abde2d8","tid":1513211,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:33:32.000Z","msg":"自推10次 2/10"},{"pid":"4ce0ad411970d43209205f450c042f0a687440f9","tid":1513211,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbqSEja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbqSEja.png&h=5fcf71d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3999bbf306c2d6aa9ff6d48cb8a78ab1bfa5baca","tid":1513211,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"自推10次 3/10"},{"pid":"ed58947c157c6e1c58f63370658df719d00e3ef5","tid":1513211,"uid":190296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"自推10次 4/10"},{"pid":"2022a64